name: Honey Eliminating
description:
Game introductionClick on various pictures of beautiful girls on the screen, find 3 identical pictures to eliminate, and after eliminating all pictures, you can pass the level and receive the corresponding CG rewards! It should be noted that each time a picture is selected, a placeholder will be consumed, and the game will end when all 7 placeholders are consumed.
Game Features
The elimination method of casual decompression. One-handed mode can be used throughout the game~Pictures of beautiful nude girls are waiting for you to eliminate and unlock~
